<main id="main" role="main">
    <h1 class="page-title"># Essays</h1>
    <p>Writing is an essential part of my process. Here you will find my unorganised jottings, thoughts, opinions, and observations in the form of essays that discuss new and old ideas from the viewpoint of an over thinker, not just about software development, and blind computing but also science, engineering, and architecture in general together with my passion for technology and technology. I am always looking to what is next and never prepared to settle; always seeking how best to leverage the technology that surrounds us, and hopefully help anyone who runs into the same sort of problems that I do.</p>
  
